{"tid":989964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師：清潔工抹窗時墮窗傷人 有機會判監","createTime":"2019-01-21T08:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T12:01:11.000Z","uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"382d159d6ace32b74980c8e3c91c5940ee9e0c74","tid":989964,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"有酒店清潔工人抹鋁窗時整個鋁窗突然飛墮街上擊斃女途人，大律師陸偉雄稱意外中抹窗的工人若有疏忽，例如曾不適當地用鋁窗來「借力」，又或是<span style=\"color: red;\">抹窗時前未有檢查清楚鋁窗是否穩固</span>，即可能觸犯了《簡易程序治罪條例》第4B條「容許物品從高處墮下」的罪名，即是指「容許自建築物掉下任何東西、或容許任何東西自建築物墬下，以致對在公眾地方之內或附近的人造成危險或損傷」，此罪最高可判監6個月及罰款1萬元，另死傷者家人亦可以向疏忽的抹窗工人索償。<br />\n<br />\n要做埋工程果份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9bdbec1980cc2ed7fdb8eff38d829db64ac412","tid":989964,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:01:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c27a3e18b42d6a0c089e902b401bceda540b5f0c","tid":989964,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb9d86d2bb41677ee7b649830201648784bbb859","tid":989964,"uid":26811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:03:10.000Z","msg":"咁做驗窗工程果個洗唔洗拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2d1096d00695fb0ed4f8a5c3b883fc114cbfbb","tid":989964,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"好慘呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個清潔工"},{"pid":"917d69e46034ebe545e8284e49e6e9af4f78cf96","tid":989964,"uid":86246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb9d86d2bb41677ee7b649830201648784bbb859","tid":989964,"uid":26811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB