唔拉驗窗拉抹窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港法律世界第一"},{"pid":"72b2c40f6fd8265dd24786d9a862c9cf73c4c53c","tid":989964,"uid":183090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"要睇下有無做 routine maintenance，啲野合唔合格，如果樣樣都合格，政府化驗師又驗唔到啲乜野，個清潔工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422794a8be13186c2ed1f75b11fc0cb23ac33666","tid":989964,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"容許物品從高處墮下算係輕罪，會唔會有機會告誤殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}